item.title: Tee Time Cover
item.description:
My cover of Tee Time by Vulfpeck! Made this pretty quickly since I used sampled kick/snare. I still recorded the hihat and crash cymbal live. Most of the keyboard sounds are from the Scarbee Vintage Keys Kontakt instruments.

Instrumentation:

  • Drums (kick/snare samples from Logic, live hihat/crash)
  • Electric Bass
  • Wurlitzer w/ chorus
  • Elec. Grand Piano
  • Synth (high part)
  • Pianet w/ wah pedal
  • Clavinet w/ wah pedal
  • Tambourine
  • Organ
